  ${
    $d w x y z A $.  $d w x y z B $.  $d w y z V $.
    $( The supersets of a nonempty set which are also subsets of a given base
       set form a filter.  (Contributed by Jeff Hankins, 12-Nov-2009.)  (The
       proof was shortened by Mario Carneiro, 14-Dec-2013.) $)
    supfil $p |- ( ( A e. V /\ B C_ A /\ B =/= (/) ) ->
        ( { x e. ~P A | B C_ x } e. Fil /\ A = U. { x e. ~P A | B C_ x } ) ) $=
      ( vy vz vw wcel wss c0 w3a cv wa wb sseq2 visset a1i cvv wsbc sbcie elrab
      wne cpw crab cfil cuni wceq elpw anbi1i bitri elisset 3ad2ant1 sbcieg syl
      simp2 mpbird wn ss0 necon3ai 3ad2ant3 0ex mtbird sstr expcom 3imtr4g ssin
      wi cin biimpi anbi12i inex1 3imtr4i isfild isfildu jca ) BDHZCBIZCJUBZKZC
